          lyricsEnglish: "Pallavi:\n\nTarataramulo taragani varamai pravahistunna, Prabhuni prema manishaka mrigamai maarani gatamai payanistunnadu. Enta deema prati raktham paapamto nindukundani, Prabhu raktham e paapam kadagagaladani, nammi baptismondi brathakamani prakatistunte, ee suvarthani enta cheppina vinnollani cheviniyyani janalane emanalani taralani.\n\nCharanam:\n\nNovahu dinamulalo jala pralayapu kaalamulo, tinuchu traguchu santoshinchutu janulu kadavari dinamulalo, Prabhu Yesuni raakado mari, maarani teeruga kaalam gadupuchu unduru. Aanadu eenadu enatikintena, ee maya lokana marpu undada? Venolla devokti prakatimpadutunna, vinnolla hrudayalu chigurinchava?\n\nCharanam:\n\nJnnamu veluvadina, velugulu prasarisutunna, cheekati vashamai poyina lokam gurthichuna? Matame kadanna margam ani chebutunna, kallaku mabbulu kammari marugun padavesena. Raktham chindhi rajyanni sthapchi rakshipabadamante adhi drohama? Mee paapa haranam, naa Yesu maranam ani ghoshisthe, adhi nedu matapracharam?\n\nTarataramulu gatiyichi janaganamulu nashiyichi, paramatmani shodhince phalamulu dorakani taruvulu, anudinamuna sahiyinchina maru bhoomini talapiche rakthaputerulu, pare vanamuna dorakavu, chigurulu premato penchina vasamulu. Ippudu avi smashanamu, maarani brathukuna kratvulu, chitimantala che vrathalu.",
