          lyricsEnglish: "Mekala rakthamunandaina kodela rakthamu nandaina..\nManishiki leduga vimochana..\nRakthamu chindimpabadakunda jarugaduga papaprakshalan..\nKanuke Kreestu rakthamtho nivarana..\nMaranashasanamu vrasina vani maranamande rakshana..\nKreestu raktha tarpana nirdoshamain bali arpana..\nPrabhuve taane manakoraku jarichina atmashuddhikarana..\n\nPallavi:\nPavitra rakthadata.. prapanchapraana data..\nSarvonmata vidhata.. sajeeva nirata puneeta..\nNa jeevadhata mokshapradata maranamu gelichina rakshanakarta..\n\nCharanam:-\nLokamto erpadina bandham.. tempinadi prabutho anubandham..\nHrudayalo kalusha durgandham.. maranamane cheralo digbandham..\nAparadhamulcheta papamulacheta chachipadiyundaga\nKaruninchi maranichi rudhiraannikarshi janmanichchaduga\nPapaniyamamu teega atmaniyamamu neega\nNoru teruvani gorrega mouname vahinchega.. vyasanakrantuduga..\n\nCharanam:-\nAakasham kinda enama.. ivvanide rakshanandam..\nManakosam Kreestu baliyagam.. niswartham nityajeevaartham..\nDevuniki shatruvulamai undagane krupanu choopaduga..\nVyasnamuluvahinchi rogamulu bharichi naligipoyaduga..\nAtikramamula moolamuga gayaparachadaga\nJanula papamu bharinchaga praname dharaposenuga..\nAparadha pariharabaliga",
