          lyricsEnglish: "Daivame tana chittamuga chesega ghanamainadiga..\nMudipade dhrudamainadiga.. vidipade veelulenaadiga..\nKalalake saakaramuga okariko okaru aadharamuga..\nTallisthanamlo bharyanuga.. tandristhanamlo bhartanuga..\nNaadane swarthamu vidaga.. manadane bandhamu jathaga..\nPratidinam thegalo lathaga allukupoye chandamuga.. aa..aa..aa\n\nPallavi:\nPellante dehamulu veraina okkatiga phaliyince daiva sankalpam..\nPellante iruvuru ekamuga tandri pani jarayince goppa avakaasham..\nIhalokalo shoonyam undaga daivam talachina bandham pelliga marenuga..\n\nCharanam:-\nRendu kallu veru veru.. shiramu nadu veruparu..\nDrishyamedi choopistunna choopulu rendu jathaga cheru..\nRendu kaalulu veru veru.. okka padhamundu cheru..\nAdugu mundu venukavuthunna gamyam maatrame kalise cheru..\nIruvurokkati ekadehamai daivakutumbamu kaavalani taane jathaparichenuga...\nDehaasukhmake manuvukoraka devatanayulanu penchali daivam niyaminchenuuga..\nAdi bandhame aalumagalu anni bandhamulanu kalipae moolamai marenuga..\n\nCharanam:-\nVarunikoraku vadhuvu sanghamu..\nSiddhaparachabadithe andamu ekadehamante ardhamu\nKreesthuto sanghamu anubandham.. lobadutaye vadhuvuku ghanamu..\nVaruni prema vadhuvu swarthamu..\nKalankamu mudatalu lena pavithramaina prabhuvu shareeramu..\nTanaku thanuga vadhuvukosame samastamunu arpinchi priyavarude pranapriyu..\nMosaginchaka matadataka varuni adugu jaadalo nadiche praneshwari aa vadhuvu goppaadaina\nAa pelli marmamu Kreestu vadhuvuke saadryashamu chayaruupamu..",
